            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pizza is cooking, combine the <strong>remaining chopped garlic</strong> with your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong>, 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and 1<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> in a small bowl<strong> </strong>–<strong> </strong>this is your <strong>garlic & herb dip</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
