    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> tandoori-style free range chicken pizza</strong> with the<strong> garlic & herb dip</strong> to the side</p><p>Season with a good grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
